Random is class in java.util package which is used to generate random numbers
Random class has non static method
 * nextInt()
 * nextInt(bound)
 which can be used to generate random numbers.

 Random r=new Random();
 System.out.println(r.nextInt());       -> give any number from -2147483648 upto +2147483647
 System.out.println(r.nextInt(100));    -> give any number from 0 upto 100




